Limitations (being fully transparent)
Still needs a good initial prompt/schema (which you already provided).
On very poor-quality scanned PDFs it may need a tiny bit of human review (rare with modern exam PDFs).
Cost is higher than Level 1/2 (but for accuracy on exam papers it is worth it).
