      "marks": 22,
      "scenario": "The company is considering launching a new group Private Medical Insurance (PMI) product where premiums are paid annually, and cover is renewable each year. The insurer has asked reinsurance companies to provide quotation for this product.",
      "parts": {
        "i": {
