          "question": "List down the key exclusions for this product.",
          "sections": {
            "Indicative Solution": [
              "Key exclusions for PMI product",
              "1. Pre-existing conditions for a specified period",
              "2. Currently ongoing treatments in any hospitals",
              "3. Treatments taken overseas hospitals.",
              "4. War, terrorism & criminal acts",
              "5. Self-inflicted injury or attempted suicide",
              "6. Hazardous hobbies",
